content: Before I do that, why couldn't you anticipate that this would be a problem? It was a problem 2 times before and you keep having to revise the file. Why? I think you should be able to anticipate these types of things and think many steps ahead, quickly. What was preventing you from knowing that if write was an issue, read would be an issue? If read and write are issues, why wouldn't schema validation be an issue when you knew that was your next task? What is next for you to do? If schema is an issue, will there be another issue?
